Subject: [PATCH v19 11/18] ARM: dts: ste-href: Add reg property to the LP5521 channel nodes
Date:   Thu, 2 Apr 2020 15:43:04 -0500
Message-ID: <20200402204311.14998-12-dmurphy@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
